data.description: *Closing Cost Assistance! Welcome Home! Start the New Year in a New Home! Well-maintained 4BD 2BA Cape Cod situated on a large corner lot waiting for new owners! Home offers 1883 sq. ft. of living, & has been tastefully updated; Windows, Bathroom, Flooring, Kitchen, Roof, All New Ductwork, HVAC, Electric Range, Refrigerator, Nest Smart Programmable Wi-Fi Thermostat, Security System, All New Vapor Barrier, Front Door, some Fresh Paint, Wood Fence, Electric Water Heater, Vinyl Fl, & Restored Deck. 1st Fl w/9ft Ceilings, Breakfast Nook, 2 BD, Primary BD w/BA, Laundry Room exiting to the deck viewing a large fenced-in backyard. Square Footage includes Finished Area Upstairs; Loft, Large walk-in hall closet, 2 BD 1 w/walk-in closet, Ceiling Fans, w/7ft Ceiling throughout, & a Huge walk-in Attic at 2nd Fl level. Ring doorbell does not convey. "As is" 364 sq. ft. garage/shed but conveys without value. Near Military bases, shopping, dining, the interstate, & more. Home is move-in ready!
